function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)

	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffect(idFireMarkerRight01, idFireRight01)
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffect(idFireMarkerRight02, idFireRight02)

end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffect(idFireMarkerLeft01, idFireLeft01)
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffect(idFireMarkerLeft02, idFireLeft02)

end

--General--
	--Markers for fire FX locations
	idFireMarkerRight01 = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "Marker_Fire_01")[1]
	idFireMarkerRight02 = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "Marker_Fire_02")[1]
	idFireMarkerLeft01 = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "Marker_Fire_03")[1]
	idFireMarkerLeft02 = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "Marker_Fire_04")[1]
	
	--Fire effect
	S_FIRE_FX = Hydra.ReferenceEffectGroup("Komdor_Brazier_Fire")

	--Starting fire FX at the marker locations
	idFireRight01 = Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idFireMarkerRight01, S_FIRE_FX, true)
	idFireRight02 = Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idFireMarkerRight02, S_FIRE_FX, true)
	idFireLeft01 = Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idFireMarkerLeft01, S_FIRE_FX, true)
	idFireLeft02 = Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idFireMarkerLeft02, S_FIRE_FX, true)
